msgid "Jay CRM Assistant"
msgstr "Jay - CRM Assistent"

msgid "Jay Connection"
msgstr "Jay Verbinding"

msgid "Connect your Odoo instance to Jay AI CRM Assistant. Jay lets you manage your CRM with voice commands."
msgstr "Verbind uw Odoo-instantie met Jay AI CRM Assistent. Jay laat u uw CRM beheren met spraakopdrachten."

msgid "Jay Instance URL"
msgstr "Jay Instantie URL"

msgid "Jay Account Email"
msgstr "Jay Account E-mail"

msgid "Jay API Key"
msgstr "Jay API-sleutel"

msgid "Connected"
msgstr "Verbonden"

msgid "Test Connection"
msgstr "Verbinding testen"

msgid "Disconnect"
msgstr "Verbinding verbreken"

msgid "How it works"
msgstr "Hoe het werkt"

msgid "Voice-to-CRM"
msgstr "Spraak naar CRM"

msgid "Record a voice note in Jay, and your contacts, deals, activities, and meetings are automatically synced to Odoo."
msgstr "Neem een spraaknotitie op in Jay en uw contacten, deals, activiteiten en vergaderingen worden automatisch gesynchroniseerd met Odoo."

msgid "Supported objects"
msgstr "Ondersteunde objecten"

msgid "Contacts, Companies, Opportunities (CRM Leads), Activities, Calendar Events, and Notes."
msgstr "Contacten, Bedrijven, Kansen (CRM Leads), Activiteiten, Agenda-afspraken en Notities."

msgid "Anti-duplicate"
msgstr "Anti-duplicaat"

msgid "Jay detects existing records before creating new ones to keep your data clean."
msgstr "Jay detecteert bestaande records voordat nieuwe worden aangemaakt om uw gegevens schoon te houden."

msgid "Please fill in both the Jay Instance URL and API Key before testing."
msgstr "Vul zowel de Jay Instantie URL als de API-sleutel in voordat u test."

msgid "Connection successful"
msgstr "Verbinding geslaagd"

msgid "Jay is connected and ready to sync your CRM data."
msgstr "Jay is verbonden en klaar om uw CRM-gegevens te synchroniseren."

msgid "Disconnected"
msgstr "Verbinding verbroken"

msgid "Jay has been disconnected from Odoo."
msgstr "Jay is losgekoppeld van Odoo."
